{"tid":1814023,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下邊啲耳塞係夠勁係乜都聽唔到","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T18:03:13.000Z","uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e86712755af4ec068073d5d9a03f6f89ca1bd75","tid":1814023,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"屋企啲聲已經搞到我長期精神緊張<br />\nbudget 500-1000 <br />\n想一帶就好似聾咗咁 舒服 唔洗音樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c334468ecbb275f3614589d72a1f5331161b1a","tid":1814023,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"50ebd17d2ecb467c4710f060032e8107eb2fdbef","tid":1814023,"uid":55456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"而家間房同個廳只係隔咗一面空心牆 每次夜晚訓教個個牆完全無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a367157f587e6e277498fa8871ec8e1da1ec6d03","tid":1814023,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"買地盤佬用嗰啲"},{"pid":"a56b21f8ce45ffdbd9b60b2dc5f49a12993c7c20","tid":1814023,"uid":141681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"咩聲咁緊要"},{"pid":"b3247264747ff8fef9ce7e9ea36314fbbde0a977","tid":1814023,"uid":39180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"隔音版+3M耳罩"},{"pid":"dd912a47c3675cf9d2a084fdd5d43a9c3f97734c","tid":1814023,"uid":190739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"其實啲耳棉唔係幫得幾多，頂晒盡五成，同埋要視乎你屋企嗰種係乜嘢噪音。<br />\n<br />\n音波(傾計吵鬧聲)嘅可以盡量關窗 &amp; 搵嘢封晒啲門嚹，用&quot;白噪音&quot;再加埋耳棉應該都幫到八九成。<br />\n<br />\n物理(敲打鑽牆聲)嘅就難搞，因為啲聲會沿住啲牆係咁響甚至震，如果真係影響到工作同情緒嘅，趁呢排啲賓館平，短租一兩個月搬出去俾自己回吓氣，否則第日睇精神科醫生都唔止呢條數。"},{"pid":"0483410cde9a065f296e2ac6190389e26544c5a9","tid":1814023,"uid":127469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"3M嗰啲耳塞都幾隔聲，棉同膠都用過，可以減成29db。樓上鑽牆都隔到六、七成。<br />\n唔夠仲可以戴多個headphone或者耳罩。<br />\n隻耳塞都係10蚊8蚊，五金舖有，可以買個試吓"},{"pid":"6103c166b12c3a957d0f73efb388c080b2fe8618","tid":1814023,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ir2AmCc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fir2AmCc.jpg&h=df2b7490&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前樓上鑽嘢<br />\n買咗兩款3m耳塞，都係十幾廿蚊<br />\n黃色個果好似貴啲啲<br />\n但好似無燈色咁隔<br />\n燈色果個渣埋一舊塞入耳<br />\n好似上面巴打講咁，隔到五到六成到啦<br />\n但都好過無"}]}